==English==
===Proper noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''Pangasinan'''
# a [[province]] of the [[Philippines]] in the island of [[Luzon]]
# a [[language]] (of the [[Austronesian]] family) spoken in the Philippines, primarily in the province of Pangasinan.
# a native speaker of the Pangasinan language.
# a resident of the province of Pangasinan
# a Filipino ethnic group of the Malay race
===Adjective===
'''Pangasinan'''
# Pertaining to the people who speak the Pangasinan language and their culture.
